ass=\"flex flex-wrap gap-x-3 gap-y-2\"><time class=\"text-primary-60 text-nowrap\" datetime=\"2026-06-10T20:00:00.000Z\">Jun 10, 2026</time></span></p>\n         </div> \n        </a>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"relative mb-8 ps-6 min-w-[calc(100%/3)] ps-0 last:me-0\">\n       <div class=\"group relative\">\n        <div class=\"ease-curve-c duration-medium max-w-container-desktop relative mx-auto w-full overflow-hidden transition-opacity rounded-md [&amp;_img]:translate-0 [&amp;_video]:translate-0 [&amp;_img]:scale-100 [&amp;_img]:transition-transform [&amp;_img]:duration-300 [&amp;_video]:transition-transform [&amp;_video]:duration-200 **:data-card-media-overlay-text:scale-100 **:data-card-media-overlay-text:transition-transform **:data-card-media-overlay-text:duration-300 group-hover:[&amp;_img]:scale-102.5 group-hover:[&amp;_video]:scale-102.5 group-hover:**:data-card-media-overlay-text:scale-102.5\">\n         <div class=\"relative w-full\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1/1\">\n          <div class=\"size-full\">\n           <div class=\"group relative overflow-hidden rounded-none image-aspect-center aspect-(--image-aspect-ratio) max-h-full max-w-full bg-surface-loading\" style=\"--image-aspect-ratio:1/1\">\n            <img alt=\"Confidential submission of draft S-1 to the SEC &gt; cover image\" data-nosnippet=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"top:0;color:transparent;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1728px) 1728px, 100vw\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4a653c11-b3b2-49c2-ab61-30d5468a2900/public 640w, https://image.jido.dev/20260609202307_confidential-submission-of-draft-s-1-to-the-sec-1x1.png 750w, https://image.jido.dev/20260609202307_confidential-submission-of-draft-s-1-to-the-sec-1x1.png 828w, https://image.jido.dev/20260609202307_confidential-submission-of-draft-s-1-to-the-sec-1x1.png 1080w, https://image.jido.dev/20260609202307_confidential-submission-of-draft-s-1-to-the-sec-1x1.png 1200w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ed23bce5-4589-4cc0-1831-635d36f05600/public 1920w, https://image.jido.dev/20260609202307_confidential-submission-of-draft-s-1-to-the-sec-1x1.png 2048w, https://image.jido.dev/20260609202307_confidential-submission-of-draft-s-1-to-the-sec-1x1.png 3840w\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260609202307_confidential-submission-of-draft-s-1-to-the-sec-1x1.png\">\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <a aria-label=\"Confidential submission of draft S-1 to the SEC - Company - Jun 8, 2026\" class=\"transition ease-curve-a duration-250 duration-medium ease-curve-d block w-full pt-4 transition-[opacity,background] after:absolute after:inset-0 after:content-['']\" id=\"5aQdVyqZwW2XIQfdLaSGco\" href=\"https://openai.com/index/openai-submits-confidential-s-1/\"> \n         <div class=\"text-primary-100 relative w-full\">\n          <div class=\"mb-4 text-h5\">Confidential submission of draft S-1 to the SEC</div>\n          <p class=\"text-meta flex flex-wrap gap-x-3 gap-y-2\"><span>Company</span><span class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-x-3 gap-y-2\"><time class=\"text-primary-60 text-nowrap\" datetime=\"2026-06-08T14:00\">Jun 8, 2026</time></span></p>\n         </div> \n        </a>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "三星电子正在向韩国及全球 DX 部门的员工部署 ChatGPT Enterprise 和 Codex，这标志着 OpenAI 规模最大的企业级发布之一。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "三星电子正在向韩国及全球 DX 部门的员工部署 ChatGPT Enterprise 和 Codex，这标志着 OpenAI 规模最大的企业级发布之一。",
  "summary": "OpenAI 的官方公告详细介绍了向三星电子员工大规模部署 ChatGPT Enterprise 和 Codex 的情况。此次部署覆盖了三星电子在韩国的所有员工以及全球所有设备体验（DX）部门的员工。文章强调，这是 OpenAI 迄今为止规模最大的企业级部署之一。三星计划将这两款工具广泛应用于软件开发、市场营销、产品开发和制造等多个职能领域，以提升生产力和问题解决能力。文章还指出，Codex 正越来越多地被用于非技术性任务，目前每周有超过 500 万人使用 Codex。文章将此次部署定位为 OpenAI 与三星之间战略关系的扩展，从 AI 基础设施延伸至劳动力转型。公告还提到了其他采用 OpenAI 企业产品的韩国机构，包括 LG 电子、Kakao 和首尔国立大学。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "三星电子正在向全球大部分员工部署 ChatGPT Enterprise 和 Codex。",
      "explanation": "此次部署覆盖了韩国所有员工及全球 DX 部门，是 OpenAI 规模最大的企业级发布之一，标志着对企业级 AI 应用的重大投入。"
    },
    {
      "point": "此次部署旨在服务于公司内部的技术与非技术工作。",
      "explanation": "三星计划在软件开发、市场营销、产品开发和制造等领域使用这些工具，突显了 AI 在编程之外的广泛适用性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "OpenAI 与三星的合作关系正从 AI 基础设施扩展至劳动力转型。",
      "explanation": "此前双方的合作重点在于为 AI 供应内存半导体，如今已扩展至全公司范围内的 AI 应用，表明战略联盟正在深化。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "对 OpenAI 而言，这一历史性的部署意义非凡，因为全球科技与制造业领导者三星电子并未将 AI 视为仅限于特定团队或职能的工具，而是将其作为核心平台，用以改善全球员工的工作与创新方式。"
  ],
